title: Table Lamps
body: A table lamp that will not hurt your eyes and your budget? We have that at Mobelaris. A far-flung catalogs of the most celebrated and superior reproductions of iconic Mid-Century, Scandinavian and 20th Century Bauhaus furniture designs. Vintage and contemporary designed table lamps that lend authenticity to look and feel. All of our products are backed by manufacturer’s warranty inclusive in the reasonable prices we offer. No middlemen involved, no overpricing, only high quality reproductions.
